{"tid":2374373,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"淘汰皇馬既西乙B球隊全隊預算70萬歐元！41歲門將為功臣","createTime":"2021-01-21T07:37:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-21T22:58:41.000Z","uid":173952,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"35032a08f142f66ebbbbfcdad8d3df03d5c53ac7","tid":2374373,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T07:37:10.000Z","msg":"在西班牙盃32強，來自西乙B聯賽的艾高恩奴創造了奇蹟，他們在主場淘汰了豪門皇馬。<br />\n<br />\n  即使被罰下一人，這支球隊最終在加時賽實現絕殺，將皇馬淘汰出局。據《馬卡報》的消息，艾高恩奴的全隊預算僅為70萬歐元。<br />\n<br />\n  在艾高恩奴陣中，41歲的門將荷西-祖安是表現最搶眼的一位，他在門前幾乎無法阻擋，多次撲出華斯基斯（Lucas Vazquez）、阿辛斯奧（Marco Asensio）等人的射門。<br />\n<br />\n  皇馬派上了賓施馬（Karim Benzema）、夏薩特（Eden Hazard）、卻奧斯（Toni Kroos）、阿辛斯奧（Marco Asensio）、卡斯米路等主力球員，但也無濟於事，無法幫助皇馬擊敗艾高恩奴。"},{"pid":"9bebacb3b605dd47402c6e93030bd386af87a87c","tid":2374373,"uid":173952,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T07:38:01.000Z","msg":"一件Hazard都過億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d01421d380e21c57dc313c2d9ef1918ffe7916a","tid":2374373,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T07:38:53.000Z","msg":"有無得翻睇"},{"pid":"351e8ef3f62f6f933b68fff0f915c8e760dcb425","tid":2374373,"uid":6030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1d01421d380e21c57dc313c2d9ef1918ffe7916a","tid":2374373,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T07:38:53.000Z","msg":"有無得翻睇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T07:41:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.realmadrid.com/en/news/2021/01/20/2-1-real-madrid-crash-out-of-the-copa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.realmadrid.com%2Fen%2Fnews%2F2021%2F01%2F20%2F2-1-real-madrid-crash-out-of-the-copa&d=PT6dGXJ5JuBAxmbDRmxpcBSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=6808a9bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.realmadrid.com/en/news/2021/01/20/2-1-real-madrid-crash-out-of-the-copa</a>"},{"pid":"d2c3f678ed54b6f759bdb23053dff650a077066a","tid":2374373,"uid":53666,"like":1,"dis